Title: Секретний контакт
RewardText:
Hey there, I'm a reporter for the Eye of Azeroth.

I'm investigating some strange activity in Valdrakken. Want to help?

I've got a source, but they'll only speak to someone wearing a 'Thinking Cap'. It's supposed to focus thoughts or some such. Anyway, I made a list of the components needed and who you can get them from. 

Track them down, then we'll talk more.
